text: Dāvids Veiss (22 September 1879 - 15 June 1961) was a Latvian sports shooter. He competed in four events at the 1912 Summer Olympics, representing the Russian Empire. ==References== Category:1879 births Category:1961 deaths Category:Latvian male sport shooters Category:Russian male sport shooters Category:Olympic shooters of Russia Category:Shooters at the 1912 Summer Olympics Category:People from Jelgava Municipality
